oai_dc:dc.dc:title: The Bovine Practitioner and the Licensing of Veterinary Biologics
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Hawkins, Bert W.
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: licensing of veterinary biologics
veterinarians
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: It's a pleasure to be here today to discuss the licensing of veterinary biologics, an issue that I know has been on your minds for some time ... and on the minds of the folks at the U.S. Department of Agriculture. I think what I say today will clarify this agency's position on new legislation ... and the benefit to you ... the practitioner.
oai_dc:dc.dc:source: American Association of Bovine Practitioners Conference Proceedings; 1984; 22-23
